import pyautogui
import time

try:
    # Open Calculator via Run dialog
    pyautogui.hotkey('win', 'r')
    time.sleep(0.5)
    pyautogui.typewrite('calc')
    pyautogui.press('enter')
    time.sleep(1)

    # Type 22
    pyautogui.typewrite('22')
    time.sleep(0.2)

    # Press '+'
    pyautogui.press('+')
    time.sleep(0.2)

    # Type 24
    pyautogui.typewrite('24')
    time.sleep(0.2)

    # Press Enter to calculate
    pyautogui.press('enter')
    time.sleep(0.5)

    print("EXECUTION_SUCCESS")
except Exception as e:
    print("FAILED:", e)
